{"tid":890313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 支那人控告香港BENZ侵權","createTime":"2018-11-05T08:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T09:23:07.000Z","uid":54373,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c02d54b7cee93a773b3424bb10c4dc55ccd50851","tid":890313,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"德國名廠汽車Benz（奔馳）懷疑商標遭一間由內地人獨資持有的香港註冊公司侵權，冒充Benz名義做生意。Benz母公司上周五入稟本港高院就損失索償，並要求法庭頒佈禁制令，阻對方未經授權使用其註冊商標或假扮與正牌公司有關，並須交出或銷毀相關產品及材料。<br />\n<br />\n原告Daimler AG報稱地址在德國工業及汽車業重鎮斯圖加特（Stuttgart），控告香港公司「德國奔馳戴姆勒股份有限公司」。入稟狀指被告公司在2016年成立，唯一董事兼股東是趙勇，報住湖南省衡東縣，公司訛稱是原告在亞洲地區的獲授權代表。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀表明，印有原告商標的汽車、成衣、配飾、雨傘、袋、銀包等，自1986年起一直由在港成立的梅賽德斯－奔馳有限公司（現改名梅賽德斯－奔馳香港有限公司）負責在中國大陸及香港分銷。被告公司及其股東或董事均與原告無關。原告指，被侵權商標包括貨車牌子「Daimler」、「戴姆勒」、汽車品牌「Mercedes-Benz」、「Benz」及「奔馳」，以及由圓形包着三角星形的圖案標誌。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA2583/18】"},{"pid":"83b3a76985f0746a9c40d56e75c640da7712ba07","tid":890313,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T08:40:54.000Z","msg":"發文者標題有誤導，應為「德國Benz控強國公司盜名侵權」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001d482d7afa109c74409cc1642425710eb8da3e","tid":890313,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"支那人 fatfat了"},{"pid":"40762e88e0e61f3f2830ddbf32a8947cb5070a6b","tid":890313,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/160/d160610.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F160%2Fd160610.jpg&h=463713ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6fff4ff601d9152da502c94a79fe593e6b1d51e","tid":890313,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"有人今日打撚哂飛機話開放市場架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabe940ec5d906a2f3d5d2cbcd796ab193aec0e9","tid":890313,"uid":47259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"支那仲話同歐盟合作對抗美國, 轉個頭就響人地背後插刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93418e5dbbf1ca8c04945ab7efe2d1ee072887a","tid":890313,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"留名睇連登仔只睇標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1625eb068b56e7f3a312209fbcd2dfa57fb8d1","tid":890313,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">入稟狀指被告公司在2016年成立，唯一董事兼股東是趙勇，報住湖南省衡東縣</span><br />\n<br />\n個topic 「支那人控告香港BENZ」<br />\n<br />\n你搞到我好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de821e082ff1a1994de855d28b0d2469707f7bca","tid":890313,"uid":28599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aabe940ec5d906a2f3d5d2cbcd796ab193aec0e9","tid":890313,"uid":47259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"支那仲話同歐盟合作對抗美國, 轉個頭就響人地背後插刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"隔離有個post講日本無印同[本土無印]打官司輸左添<br />\n成個營商環境都唔係保障投資者，投乜撚野資呢"},{"pid":"dc9b456d1c255a00a607df3310c1c6fddb7d1fd0","tid":890313,"uid":72304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93418e5dbbf1ca8c04945ab7efe2d1ee072887a","tid":890313,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"留名睇連登仔只睇標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"成班盲亨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal